N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4626.3 - Licensee to be informed of revocation proceedings

State Regulations

Notice of proceedings to suspend or revoke a license or
levy a fine shall be in writing to the licensee informing it of the grounds
thereof and the date and place set for hearing thereon. Notes
